Docs.summary: A generic hash function, designed to return equal hash values for items that are equal according to the "=" operator. By default it will use structural hashing for F# union, record and tuple types, hashing the complete contents of the type. The exact behaviour of the function can be adjusted on a type-by-type basis by implementing GetHashCode for each type.
